            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üéØ</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Practical Focus</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                Real solutions for real classrooms
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">üåü</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Excellence</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                Curated, high-quality resources only
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl mb-4">ü§ù</div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Community</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
                Building connections amongst educators
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Book Section -->
        <div id="buy" class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16 scroll-mt-24">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
              The Book: "Generative AI for Teachers"
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              Our comprehensive guide provides secondary school and IB teachers with practical strategies 
              for integrating generative AI tools into their daily teaching practice. From lesson planning 
              to assessment, discover how AI can enhance rather than replace your expertise.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">320+ pages of practical guidance</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
